.iframe-container

	.main-container

		h1.page-title Helpers



		article#background-color.article

			p Helpers or utlity classes should generally be used sparingly. All helper class attributes are suffixed with an !important flag to avoid specificity issues.

			h3 Background Color
			p Generates a background-color helper for all colors specified in the palette category in the settings map. To append the colour category and name to the helper. 

			pre
				code.language-html
					| &lt;div class="background-brand-primary"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

			pre
				code.language-scss
					| .background-brand-primary {
					|  background-color: #F5F5F5 !important;
					| }

		article#borders.article
			h3#borders Borders
			p Adds or removes a keyline to a given element. The border color used is the keyline value specified in the settings map.
			ul.bullet-list.margin-bottom-double
				li border-left
				li border-top
				li border-right
				li border-bottom
				li border-all
				li no-border
			pre
				code.language-html
					| &lt;div class="background-brand-primary"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

			pre
				code.language-scss
					| .background-brand-primary {
					|  background-color: #F5F5F5 !important;
					| }


