		article#text-align.article
			h3 Typography

			p <span class="class">.text-{helper}</span>.

			h4 Alignment
			p These classes are for horizontally aligning content:

			ul.bullet-list
				li left
				li right
				li center

			h4 Size

			p Helpers for creating the various text sizes specified in your settings file.

			ul.bullet-list
				li x-small
				li small
				li base
				li medium
				li medium-large
				li large
				li x-large

			h4 Transform

			ul.bullet-list
				li uppercase
